               <msContents class="#STM">
                  <summary><p>Unidentified text, apparently named <title xml:lang="ta">Pāratavilācam</title>. Contains vers and prose portions, designations of <foreign xml:lang="ta">rākam</foreign> and <foreign xml:lang="ta">tāḷam</foreign>.</p>
<p>Wrongly identified as the <title xml:lang="ta">Naiṭatam</title> by Feer in Vinson et al. (1866-) and by Cabaton (1912).</p>
<p>Description based on the digital images available on Gallica.</p>
<p>Dimensions after Cabaton (1912).</p>  
                  </summary>
                  
